# Theming Guide for FalVibeExpoReact

The app supports light and dark themes using system color scheme.

- Use [components/ThemedView.tsx](mdc:components/ThemedView.tsx) for themed views.
- Use [components/ThemedText.tsx](mdc:components/ThemedText.tsx) for themed text.
- Fetch themed colors with [hooks/useThemeColor.ts](mdc:hooks/useThemeColor.ts).
- Detect color scheme with [hooks/useColorScheme.ts](mdc:hooks/useColorScheme.ts).
- Color definitions: [constants/Colors.ts](mdc:constants/Colors.ts).

Always apply theming to maintain consistent UI across modes.
